<plot>Sybil is an older widow about to go on a vacation with her friend Eleanor, but her dead husband Manny shows up. He does a little kvetching about not being invited along, and the still-mourning Sybil considers not leaving so that she can stay with him. Maybe Sybil will figure out what the term "land of the living" really means.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?420014</url></doc>
